WEBVTT

00:05:29.200 --> 00:05:32.600
I am not talking about the future;
this is happening now.

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:37.040
So we should, on the internet, share
only as much of our identity as necessary.

00:05:37.880 --> 00:05:41.119
There are some easy ways to hide
things; it’s not difficult at all.

00:05:41.143 --> 00:05:45.986
To begin with, on your phone,
delete all the apps you don’t use.

00:05:45.986 --> 00:05:49.496
Keep the privacy settings
on your phone at a high level.

00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:52.430
For the websites and apps
you frequently use,

00:05:52.430 --> 00:05:56.190
understand their privacy levels
and then use them.

00:05:57.320 --> 00:06:00.576
For free Wi-Fi, do not
so easily give out your details;